quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  49,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  49,1,momino! ( kisi baat ke jawab mein ) khuda aur is ke rasool se pehlay nah bol utha karo aur khuda se drtay raho. be shak khuda santa jaanta hai
  49,2,ae ahal imaan! apni aawazian paighambar ki aawaz se onche nah karo aur jis terhan aapas mein aik dosray se zor se boltay ho ( is terhan ) un ke rubaroo zor se nah bola karo ( aisa nah ho ) ke tumahray aamaal zaya ho jaien aur tum ko khabar bhi nah ho
  49,3,jo log paighambar khuda ke samnay dubi aawaz se boltay hain khuda ne un ke dil taqwa ke liye aazma liye hain. un ke liye bakhshish aur ajar azeem hai
  49,4,jo log tum ko hujron ke bahar se aawaz dete hain un mein aksar be aqal hain
  49,5,aur agar woh sabr kiye rehtay yahan taq ke tum khud nikal kar un ke paas atay to yeh un ke liye behtar tha. aur khuda to bakhsnay wala meharban hai
  49,6,momino! agar koi badkirdar tumahray paas koi khabar le kar aeye to khoob tahaqeeq karliya karo ( mbada ) ke kisi qoum ko nadani se nuqsaan pouncha do. phir tum ko apne kiye par nadim hona parre
  49,7,aur jaan rakho ke tum mein khuda ke peghamber hain. agar bohat si baton mein woh tumhara kaha maan liya karen to tum mushkil mein par jao lekin khuda ne tum ko imaan Aziz bana diya aur is ko tumahray dilon mein saja diya aur kufar aur gunah aur nafarmani se tum ko bezaar kardiya. yahi log raah hadaayat par hain
  49,8,( yani ) khuda ke fazl aur ahsaan se. aur khuda jan-nay wala ( aur ) hikmat wala hai
  49,9,aur agar mominoun mein se koi do fareeq aapas mein lar parrin to un mein sulah kara do. aur agar aik fareeq dosray par zayad-ti kere to zayad-ti karne walay se lrho yahan taq ke woh khuda ke hukum ki taraf rujoo laaye. pas jab woh rujoo laaye to woh dono fareeq mein masawaat ke sath sulah kara do aur insaaf se kaam lau. ke khuda insaaf karne walon ko pasand karta hai
  49,10,momin to aapas mein bhai bhai hain. to apne do bhaiyon mein sulah kara diya karo. aur khuda se drtay raho taakay tum par rehmat ki jaye
  49,11,momino! koi qoum kisi qoum se tamaskhur nah kere mumkin hai ke woh log un se behtar hon aur nah aurtain aurton se ( tamaskhur karen ) mumkin hai ke woh un se achi hon. aur apne ( momin bhai ) ko aib nah lagao aur nah aik dosray ka bura naam rakho. imaan laane ke baad bura naam ( rakhna ) gunah hai. aur jo tauba nah karen woh zalim hain
  49,12,ae ahal imaan! bohat gumaan karne se Ihtiraz karo ke baaz gumaan gunah hain. aur aik dosray ke haal ka tajassus nahkiya karo aur nah koi kisi ki gheebat kere.kiya tum mein se koi is baat ko pasand kere ga ke apne marey hue bhai ka gosht khaye? is se to tum zaroor nafrat karo ge. ( to gheebat nah karo ) aur khuda ka dar rakho be shak khuda tauba qubool karne wala meharban hai
  49,13,logo! hum ne tum ko aik mard aur aik aurat se pedakiya aur tumhari qoumain aur qabeeley banaye. taakay aik dosray ko shanakht karo. aur khuda ke nazdeek tum mein ziyada izzat wala woh hai jo ziyada parhaizgaar hai. be shak khuda sab kuch jan-nay wala ( aur ) sab se khabardaar hai
  49,14,dehati kehte hain ke hum imaan le aeye. keh do ke tum imaan nahi laaye ( balkay yun ) kaho ke hum islam laaye hain aur imaan to hunooz tumahray dilon mein daakhil hi nahi howa. aur tum khuda aur is ke rasool ki farmabardari karo ge to khuda tumahray aamaal se kuch kam nahi kere ga. be shak khuda bakhsnay wala meharban hai
  49,15,momin to woh hain jo khuda aur is ke rasool par imaan laaye phir shak mein nah parre aur khuda ki raah mein maal aur jaan se larray. yahi log ( imaan ke ) sachey hain
  49,16,un se kahokiya tum khuda ko apni deendari jatlatay ho. aur khuda to asmano aur zameen ki sab cheezon se waaqif hai. aur khuda har shai ko jaanta hai
  49,17,yeh log tum par ahsaan rakhtay hain ke musalman hogaye hain. keh do ke apne musalman honay ka mujh par ahsaan nah rakho. balkay khuda tum par ahsaan rakhta hai ke is ne tumhe imaan ka rasta dekhaya bashart e kay tum sachey ( musalman ) ho
  49,18,be shak khuda asmano aur zameen ki posheeda baton ko jaanta hai aur jo kuch tum karte ho usay daikhta hai
